              &quot;confidence&quot;: 0.9829583
            }
          ],
          &quot;languageCode&quot;: &quot;en-us&quot;
        },
      ]
    }

You can find more about how to make HTTP Requests to the Speech to Text API in the follow documentation on the &quot;PROTOCOL&quot; tab:
